Pfsense was configured to use the DHCP service

How to configure: 
  Log into pfsense using a browser
  Select Services > DHCP Server 
  Under LAN:
  Enable DHCP on LAN
  Set Range of Usable Hosts (10.0.5.150 - 10.0.5.175)
  Set DNS Servers (10.0.5.5)
  ENABLE TIME FORMAT CHANGE TRUST ME!!!
  Satically Assingn Mappings if Needed
